@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ywskpf(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (wp.sin(v0) / ((v0 + 0.92 * v2 + 0.42) / wp.exp(v2 + 0.06)))
    tmp = (tmp - (tmp * tmp))
    v1 = wp.abs(wp.sin((v2 + 0.50 * v0 + 0.19)))
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.cos(wp.abs(v2 + 0.35)))
    data[tid] = v0
